snippet.textDisplay:
on facebook --
BarmerBoys

Biography
The group formed in 2011, and their music is a harmonic blend of distinct performance styles and personalities. 

Mangey Khan, who belongs to a family of illustrious singers, has an electrifying voice and is equally at home singing traditional Marwari wedding songs or belting out Sufi qawwalis. He also plays the harmonium (similar to the reed organ or the accordion).
